metadata.name: BANTA BEAR#1
metadata.description: Banta Bear is a collection with 10K collections. The reason we created is that we have phanta bear before. And they face an internal problem, and the way how they solve the problem makes us panic and anxious. So we decided to make the bear. We think that it expresses our dissatisfaction and the flipping price is too high at that moment, not enough information. In the end, we still hope the phanta bear could be better. If you feel interesting about our art.Come and visit our discord channel.There will be events holding.
